Notes for netbsd libs:

FLTK:
configure options: --x-includes=/usr/X11R6/include/ --x-libraries=/usr/X11R6/lib --enable-gl=no
version used: fltk-1.1.6

CDK:
configure options: --with-ncurses  --with-curses-dir=/home/rick/div/ncurses-5.4 --without-curses
version used: cdk-5.0-20050424
other: manually changed HAVE_CURSES_H to HAVE_NCURSES_H in cdk/cdk_config.h(would conflict with native curses library otherwise), ran 'strip -d' on the lib

ncurses:
configure options: --without-curses-h --enable-termcap
version used: ncurses-5.4
other: had to enable termcap fallback, since no terminfo exists by default

